Clone a Standard Bot as an Enhanced Bot

To upgrade your existing conversation designs with rich content and more flexible routing, clone a standard bot as an enhanced bot. Einstein Bots is available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience.

REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS

* Available in: Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions
* To use enhanced Messaging channels with Enhanced Bots: view required editions.
* User permissions needed:
	+ Customize Application
	+ Modify Metadata
	+ Manage Bots

When you clone a standard bot as an enhanced bot, the guided cloning experience reconfigures features that work differently for enhanced bots. Learn more in About Cloning a Standard Bot as an Enhanced Bot.

Turn on Omni-Channel to allow Salesforce to create Omni-Channel flows to route conversations to and from your bot. Visit Route Conversations to and from Your Enhanced Bot to get an overview of inbound and outbound routing with Omni-Channel Flow.

To clone a standard bot:

1. Go to the Einstein Bot Setup page and find the standard bot you want to clone in the My Bots list.
2. Click the dropdown and select Clone.
3. Enter a unique bot display name and API name.
4. Under Select a type of bot, select Enhanced: A bot that uses flows for more flexible routing. Then click Next.
5. Review the details about how we configure your new botâ€™s context variables, conversation routing, and custom dialogs.

Save your changes. The system clones the bot and enters the Bot Builder Dialogs page.

CONFIGURE ROUTING FOR YOUR BOT

* INBOUND: SEND CONVERSATIONS TO YOUR ENHANCED BOT
* OUTBOUND: TRANSFER CONVERSATIONS FROM YOUR ENHANCED BOT

When you clone a standard bot as an enhanced bot, we create simple inbound and outbound Omni-Channel flows for your bot. You can customize and activate these flows in Flow Builder.

About Cloning a Standard Bot as an Enhanced Bot
